rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, come on, Seori!
This way!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0002
rows.name:
Don't rush me, Onee-chan.
The scenery isn't going anywhere.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0003
rows.name:
Don't be silly! What if we miss
some kind of amazing moment?!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0004
rows.name: C'mon, get moving!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0005
rows.name: Hmph...

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0006
rows.name: Mikumari looks pretty excited, huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0007
rows.name: Mikumari's getting totally excited, huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0008
rows.name: Mikumari seems quite excited.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0009
rows.name: Mikumari looks dead excited, huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0010
rows.name:
Yeah... Well, I mean... She's getting
a bit carried away, if you ask me.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0011
rows.name:
Honestly...
I wish she'd calm down a bit.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0012
rows.name:
You say that, but I get the feeling
you're enjoying yourself too.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0013
rows.name:
You say that, but I bet you're enjoying
yourself just as much really!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0014
rows.name:
So you say, but it seems to me that
you're enjoying yourself quite a bit too.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0015
rows.name:
You say that, but you're having
a good time too. Am I wrong?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0016
rows.name: Do you think so?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0017
rows.name: I suppose you might be right.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0018
rows.name:
I've got to spend plenty of time with
Onee-chan lately. That's always good.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0019
rows.name: I really like being with her.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0020
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0021
rows.name: It's almost like you're real sisters.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0022
rows.name: I guess you really get each other now.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0023
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0024
rows.name: You're just like human sisters, huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0025
rows.name: You really get each other now, huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0026
rows.name: What shall I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0027
rows.name: It's as if you're real sisters.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0028
rows.name: You've come to understand each other.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0029
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0030
rows.name: You're like real sisters, aren't you?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0031
rows.name: I guess you really get each other now.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0032
rows.name:
You think so...? It's hard for
me to tell, personally.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0033
rows.name:
It's just, well, you know how she's
constantly acting before she thinks.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0034
rows.name:
I'm always so nervous for her, I can't
leave her alone for a moment.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0035
rows.name:
Yet somehow, I don't feel like
that's a bad thing. It's always
kind of fun to be around her.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0036
rows.name:
I guess you're always thinking
about each other, huh? I'm sure
Mikumari feels the same way.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0037
rows.name:
Sounds like you've always got each
other on the mind. I bet Mikumari
thinks about you a lot, too.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0038
rows.name:
I suppose you must always be thinking
about each other. Her as well as you.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0039
rows.name:
I reckon you've always got each
other on the mind. I'd say she
thinks about you a lot, too.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0040
rows.name:
I guess you're right... Maybe that's
what being sisters is about.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0041
rows.name:
But, Mikumari is the older sister here, yet it's me
who seems to be worrying about her...

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0042
rows.name:
Haha! That's true... But she wouldn't
be Mikumari otherwise, right?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0043
rows.name:
Haha! Yeah... But I guess that's
what makes her Mikumari!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0044
rows.name:
Ha ha... True enough. But I suppose
that's all part of Mikumari's charm.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0045
rows.name:
Haha! Yeah... But she wouldn't be
Mikumari otherwise, would she?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0046
rows.name: You think so?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0047
rows.name:
Sometimes I'm not sure. I still don't feel
like I know everything about her.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0048
rows.name:
And I'm sure she doesn't always get
everything about me.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0049
rows.name: But, she said something once...

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0050
rows.name:
She told me, we may not have any
memories, but it's no use worrying
about what we don't have.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0051
rows.name:
If we know nothing about each other's
pasts... That just means we have a
clean slate for the future.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0052
rows.name:
Every moment we spend together now
is a new memory for us to share.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0053
rows.name:
Wow... That's deep, but I can see
how it's the kind of thing she'd say.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0054
rows.name:
Huh... Pretty deep stuff! But that
attitude is Mikumari all over.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0055
rows.name:
I see... Perhaps that attitude is why
Mikumari is such a lovely person.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0056
rows.name:
Hah! Deep stuff, coming from her.
But somehow, that's Mikumari all over.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0057
rows.name: Exactly. And that's why...

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0058
rows.name:
That's why the time that I spend with
her is so special to me.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0059
rows.name:
And at the same time, my Driver is
important to me, too!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0060
rows.name:
I couldn't be more grateful to you
for bringing us back together.

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0061
rows.name: Hey, Seori! What're you up to?

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0062
rows.name:
Quit getting all cozy with your Driver
and get over here already!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0063
rows.name: Cozy? What's that supposed to mean?!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0064
rows.name:
C'mon, over here, look!
Quickly!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0066
rows.name: Hey, you too! Let's check it out!

rows.label: kizunatalk064_msg0067
rows.name:
This is gonna be a memory
for all three of us to treasure!
